media:group.media:title: Worship Talks - Sunday 10th September 2023
media:group.media:description:
Worship talks from Trinity United Reformed Church, High Wycombe What we spoke and prayed about 1 year ago 🗓️. How does it relate to now, is it still relevant?
#JacobsLadder #Genesis #BibleStory #Godsplan #HeavenandEarth #SpiritualSymbol #JesusChrist #LadderofLife #FaithandHope #ChristianDevotional
Jacob is a sad and lonely figure. Jacob is a key player in God's Plan of Salvation or the world. Jacob has been living up to his name for Jacob is a man who makes sure he gets what he wants irrespective of Deceit and the cost to anyone else. Jacob’s Ladder is a symbol of the connection between Heaven and Earth. It is also a symbol of the presence of God in our lives. Jesus is the ladder spanning Heaven and Earth.
